{"ID":"20260605143532-9vvd1yd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605143532-9vvd1yd","title":"2022年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605143612-eth7q7o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-eth7q7o","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"画眉鸟"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-hfqpb2s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-hfqpb2s","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"欧阳修"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-ci6b0oe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-ci6b0oe","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百啭千声随意移，山花红紫树高低。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-95bc5m1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-95bc5m1","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"始知锁向金笼听，不及林间自在啼。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-3trzeox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-3trzeox","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"画眉禽"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-v734oxg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-v734oxg","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文同"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-534t94f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-534t94f","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽日闲窗生好风，一声初听下高笼。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143612-kt9pxfl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143612-kt9pxfl","updated":"20260605143549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公庭事简人皆散，如在千岩万壑中。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143532-6xwqocf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605143532-6xwqocf","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605143620-1htqnxt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143620-1htqnxt","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．下列对这两首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605143620-i59rswr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143620-i59rswr","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．欧诗和文诗题目大体相同，都是以画眉鸟作为直接描写对象的咏物诗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143620-ttbc7cg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143620-ttbc7cg","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．欧诗所写的画眉鸟在花木间自由飞行，文诗中的画眉鸟则在笼中饲养。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143620-fzk0hom","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143620-fzk0hom","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．欧诗认为鸟笼内外的画眉鸟，其鸣叫声有差别，而文诗对此并未涉及。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143620-fasrula","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143620-fasrula","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．欧诗中的“林间”与文诗中的“千岩万壑”具有大致相同的文化含意。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143620-ecgrygm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143620-ecgrygm","updated":"20260605143620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．这两首诗中，画眉鸟所起的作用并不相同。请简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143532-njdn3vt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605143532-njdn3vt","updated":"20260605143633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605143532-vbn4daf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143532-vbn4daf","updated":"20260605143633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．A    15．①欧诗托物言志，通过对比画眉鸟在不同的环境中的叫声，将画眉鸟作为寄托情怀的对象，抒发的是诗人归隐山林、挣脱羁绊、向往自由的感情。②文诗对画眉进行侧面描写，通过对比“公庭事简人皆散”前后对画眉鸟鸣声的听觉感受，衬托出了诗人高洁出尘、闲散淡泊、襟韵洒落的人物形象。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143532-cyid62v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605143532-cyid62v","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605143646-m3i4q9x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143646-m3i4q9x","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌表达技巧，理解诗歌内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143646-003imb2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143646-003imb2","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“都是以画眉鸟作为直接描写对象”说法错误。文诗中主要描写画眉鸟的叫声，初听之时，声音来自“高笼”之中；但等到诗人了却简单的公事，众人散尽之后，衙署清幽安静，则如同置身于“千岩万壑中”一般，从而衬托出诗人不慕名利、淡泊悠远的人物形象，但并没有直接对画眉鸟进行描写。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143646-3hiwygh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143646-3hiwygh","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143646-xa55g6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143646-xa55g6a","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌事物形象的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143646-0n9pjf1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143646-0n9pjf1","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"欧诗以画眉鸟为直接描写对象，托物言志，写诗人听见画眉鸟在山林繁花之间千啼百啭，才知道笼中画眉的叫声，远比不上它在山间的自由歌唱那么悦耳动听。在本诗中，诗人对画眉鸟进行正面描写，通过对比画眉鸟在“山花红紫树高低”和“锁向金笼”两种截然不同的环境中的叫声，将画眉鸟作为寄托情怀的对象，表面写鸟，实则写人，抒发的是诗人归隐山林、挣脱羁绊、向往自由的感情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143646-8e8smrk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143646-8e8smrk","updated":"20260605143646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文诗虽以画眉为题，但并未具体地描写画眉鸟的形象和叫声，而是进行侧面描写，重点渲染了“公庭事简人皆散”之后，初听上去仍在“高笼”中的画眉鸣声此时听起来却如同置身于“千岩万壑中”，悠远空旷，清幽寂静。本诗通过对比“公庭事简人皆散”前后对画眉鸟鸣声的听觉感受，烘托出了诗人高洁出尘、闲散淡泊、襟韵洒落的人物形象，表现诗人在公务闲暇时悠然自得的状态。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143532-tjkkyrw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143532-tjkkyrw","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}